  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators believe that regulated oxygen-enriched negative Pressure Therapy (RO-NPT)
      will be beneficial in the reduction or elimination of anaerobic infection in hard-to-heal
      soft tissue wounds.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
